<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ḥb ʿẓym qd smạ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ḥb ʿẓym qd smạ ʿn kl ḥb fy ạlwry̱ ạ̉ḥb fạdynạ ạlʿjyb mḥqqaⁿạ kl ạlmny̱
 mn frṭ ḥbh lnạ ʿnạ ṣlybh ạʿtly̱
 2- ḥb ʿẓym qd ʿlạ blạ ḥdwd dạʿyạ
 ạsry̱ ạlrdy̱ jmyʿhm bṭlfh mnạdyạ
 bdẖlk bạlḥb dmy̱ mạ rd ḥby yạ try̱
 3- hl tftḥn qlbk lmn ạ̉ḥb ạ̉wlạaⁿ
 tʿṭyh ạ̉gẖly̱ mạ lk thdyh ʿmrạ kạmlạ
 nẓyr dẖạ ạlḥb ạldẖy mn ạ̉jlk dẖạq ạlrdy̱</lyrics>
